OL,3,C'Profound injustice' for woman who had
OL,4,Chysterectomy without giving consent
OL,6,FAn investigation was launched by the
OL,7,FPublic Services Ombudsman for Wales
OL,8,Fafter Ms A complained about her care
OL,9,Ffrom BCUHB and Liverpool University
OL,10,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust.
OL,12,FHer concerns included the management
OL,13,Fand care she received following
OL,14,Fsurgery for her inflammatory bowel
OL,15,Fdisease in 2019; whether she was
OL,16,Fproperly consented for surgery in
OL,17,FMarch 2022; as well as postoperative
OL,18,Fcare and treatment and the handling of
OL,19,Fher complaint.
