OL,4,Chysterectomy without giving consent
OL,6,FFollowing the investigation, the
OL,7,FOmbudsman concluded 'significant
OL,8,Fshortcomings' in the patient's care
OL,9,Fwere caused by failings across various
OL,10,Faspects of her treatment.
OL,12,FThis included failings in colorectal
OL,13,Fcare, and in relation to
OL,14,Fgynaecological referrals
OL,15,Finvestigations and treatment
OL,16,Fundertaken by another English Trust.
