OL,3,C'Profound injustice' for woman who had
OL,4,Chysterectomy without giving consent
OL,6,FMeanwhile, Dr Jim Gardner, Group Chief
OL,7,FMedical Officer for NHS University
OL,8,FHospitals of Liverpool Group, which
OL,9,Fruns the Royal Liverpool University
OL,10,FHospital and Liverpool Women's
OL,11,FHospital, said: "On behalf of NHS
OL,12,FUniversity Hospitals of Liverpool
OL,13,FGroup, I apologise for the failings
OL,14,Fidentified in the report and I
OL,15,Facknowledge the profound effects they
OL,16,Fhave had, and continue to have, on the
OL,17,Fpatient and her family.
