OL,6,F"This was a very complex case
OL,7,Finvolving multiple clinicians and
OL,8,Fdepartments across several hospitals.
OL,9,FWe have already made improvements, and
OL,10,Fwe will ensure that the lessons
OL,11,Flearned from this are shared with our
OL,12,Fclinical teams to prevent something
OL,13,Flike this happening again.
OL,15,F"We are working through the
OL,16,Fombudsman's recommendations, which we
OL,17,Faccept in full."
